@page "/facilities"

<PageTitle>Facilities</PageTitle>

<div class="page-container">
    <h3 class="facilities-header">Facilities</h3>
    <hr />

    <div class="facilities-grid">
        <div class="facilities-text">
            <p>At Kelburg Hotel, we believe a stay should be more than just a place to rest — it should be an experience.</p>
            <p>Whether you're here for business, relaxation, or an unforgettable getaway, our one-of-a-kind facilities are designed to surprise, delight, and maybe even confuse you (in the best way possible).</p>

            <p><strong>We offer facilities such as:</strong></p>
            <ul class="facilities-list">
                <li>Fusion Gym</li>
                <li>Infinity Pool</li>
                <li>Cage-fighting Ring</li>
                <li>Camel Stable</li>
                <li>Waterpark</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="facilities-images">
            <img src="images/facilities/FusionGym.png" alt="Fusion Gym" />
            <img src="images/facilities/Waterpark.jpg" alt="Waterpark" />
            <img src="images/facilities/UfcCage.png" alt="Cage-fighting Ring" />
            <img src="images/facilities/Camelstable.png" alt="Camel Stable" />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>